description: It´s "warehouse-day" again. I will probably never understand why we have so many applicants for those jobs. On the other hand they don´t require too many qualifications. The guys applying are usually kinda handsome. Sometimes a bit older but still very nice. But the first guy was quite aggressive after I told him about my offer. He threatened to call the police - but there is nothing illegal about my proposal, so I didn´t get his point. The second one was probably too shy. I don´t know if he has something to hide in his pants. But still sad that he also didn´t agree. Finally a nice guy came in. Blond and desperately into this job. It took me a while to assure him that I am not faking and that he will really get the contract once he agrees to show me his body.
title: Dirty Scout 19
